---
title: Italian Beef Ragu & Gnocchi with Parmesan Cheese
description: This sumptuous pasta is absolute decadence in a bowl. From rich ragu to pillowy gnocchi, you may have to throw dice for the leftovers! And get ready to learn our favourite technique for gnocchi - with no pre-boiling required you'll fry them into delicious golden morsels.
